#

Mushroom and Garlic Toast

20 min
$5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Gluten (if using regular bread)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

ItalianAmerican

Course:

AppetizerSnack

Tags:

QuickEasySnack

Description

Savory mushroom and garlic spread on toasted bread, perfect for a quick snack or appetizer.

Ingredients

  • sliced mushrooms: 2 cups
  • garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • bread (your choice): 4 slices
  • fresh parsley (optional): for garnish
